1. *Neprijatno* je čuti istinu. (It is unpleasant to hear the truth.)

2. Ona je osetila *neprijatnost* u sobi. (She felt the discomfort in the room.)

3. On je bio *neprijatan* prema njoj. (He was unpleasant towards her.)

4. Ona je bila *neprijatna* prema meni. (She was rude to me.)

5. *Neprijatno* je bilo čekati ga sat vremena. (It was unpleasant to wait for him for an hour.)

6. On je osetio *neprijatnost* u njenom glasu. (He felt the unpleasantness in her voice.)